            Weekly Description
          </h3>
          <p>
            This week will be a introduction to our module. We'll get closer to our peers, 
            you'll get to know more about your instructor. We'll start by talking about mapping and cartography.
            Before we can get into reintepreting culture <em>through</em> mapping, we must first talk about the culture <em>of</em> mapping.
          </p>
        </section>
